{"id":409302,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/10/【网络民议】共青团先撕任大炮，再战潘石屹/","date":"2015-10-06T04:05:43Z","modified":"2017-03-02T09:26:47Z","title":"【网络民议】共青团先撕任大炮，再战潘石屹","content":"<p>10月5日，知名地产商潘石屹发微博谈庚子赔款，称：“麻省理工学院一位教授告诉我，现在资助中国留学生的钱，是当年庚子赔款的钱。” 对此，@共青团福建省委评论：“拿着国耻，谢恩典也是少见”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.27.16.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409314\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.27.16.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.27.16\" width=\"495\" height=\"518\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.27.16.png 495w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.27.16-287x300.png 287w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.10.431.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409317\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.10.431.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.10.43\" width=\"550\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.10.431.png 592w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.10.431-300x189.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.05.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409312\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.05.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.13.05\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.05.png 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.05-300x170.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.33.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409313\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.33.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.13.33\" width=\"550\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.33.png 601w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.13.33-300x160.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.01.45.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409310\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.01.45.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.01.45\" width=\"550\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.01.45.png 601w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.01.45-300x270.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>潘石屹接着发微博回应，提及<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/09/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E4%BB%BB%E5%BF%97%E5%BC%BA%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E6%8E%A5%E7%8F%AD%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F/\">前几日任志强就“共产主义接班人”这一提法激辩共青团一事</a>，称“@任志强惹了你们，你们去折腾@任志强去。” 有网友评论：“撕不过大炮，转移火力了。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.35.22.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-409319\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/10/Screen-Shot-2015-10-05-at-下午8.35.22.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-05 at 下午8.35.22\" width=\"495\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net